<h2>comorbidity: Computing Comorbidity Scores</h2>
<p>Computing comorbidity scores such as the weighted Charlson score
  (Charlson, 1987 &lt;<a href="https://doi.org/10.1016%2F0021-9681%2887%2990171-8">doi:10.1016/0021-9681(87)90171-8</a>&gt;) and the Elixhauser
  comorbidity score (Elixhauser, 1998 &lt;<a href="https://doi.org/10.1097%2F00005650-199801000-00004">doi:10.1097/00005650-199801000-00004</a>&gt;)
  using ICD-9-CM or ICD-10 codes (Quan, 2005 &lt;<a href="https://doi.org/10.1097%2F01.mlr.0000182534.19832.83">doi:10.1097/01.mlr.0000182534.19832.83</a>&gt;).</p>
